<% page_title('Browse texts') %>
<div class="browse-all-texts">
  <h2>Browse all Texts</h2>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="browse-texts__description  browse-page__description col-md-10">
      Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.
      Vivamus sagittis lacus vel augue laoreet rutrum faucibus dolor auctor. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis
      parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur
      ridiculus mus.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="pagination-stuff col-md-10">
      <%= paginate @texts %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12" id="search-results">
      <% texts_by_author(@texts).each do |author| %>
        <h3><%= render 'shared/topic_author', text: author[:texts][0] %></h3>
        <ul class="list-group">
          <% author[:texts].each do |text| %>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <%= render 'shared/text_tombstone', text: text %>
            </li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      <% end %>

      <%= paginate @texts %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>